A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to the Hathaway scholarship program;
2 clarifying that the definition of "certificate" includes
3 trade certificate programs; requiring students to work or
4 attend graduate school in Wyoming for a specified time in
5 order to receive a Hathaway scholarship; requiring
6 rulemaking; specifying applicability; and providing for
7 effective dates.
8
9 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
10
11 Section 1. W.S. 21-16-1301(a)(iv) and
12 21-16-1303(b)(intro) and by creating a new paragraph (iv)
13 are amended to read:
14
15 21-16-1301. Definitions.
1 HB0036

