1 21-16-1304 and 21-16-1305 to any student who has been
2 accepted by and enrolls in an eligible institution to
3 pursue a degree or certificate, and who meets the following
4 qualifications and requirements:
5
6 (iv) The student enters into an agreement with
7 the department under which the student agrees to actively
8 engage in work in Wyoming for one (1) year or attend
9 graduate school at the University of Wyoming for one (1)
10 year, for every four (4) academic semesters or portions
11 thereof in which a Hathaway scholarship was received. The
12 department shall establish by rule the commencement of the
13 period for undertaking the requirements of this paragraph,
14 which shall begin not later than one (1) year after the
15 completion of the last semester in which a Hathaway
16 scholarship was received.
17
18 Section 2. The agreement required under W.S.
19 21-16-1303(b)(iv) as created by section 1 of this act shall
20 apply to any scholarship first awarded under the Hathaway
21 scholarship program on or after July 1, 2025.
